## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on parliamentary scrutiny. Some sources may not reflect the most current developments or reforms in parliamentary processes. Additionally, the effectiveness of scrutiny can vary significantly across different political contexts and legislative bodies, which may not be fully captured in this analysis. Further research and updated data would be beneficial for a more detailed understanding of the effectiveness of parliamentary scrutiny.